Requirements
----------------------------------

* Python 2.7: http://www.python.org/
* PyCrypto: https://www.dlitz.net/software/pycrypto/
* GCC/G++: http://gcc.gnu.org/
* Boost: http://www.boost.org/

Included with FTE
* openfst (not in repos): http://www.openfst.org/
* gmpy (need source, specific version): https://code.google.com/p/gmpy/
* re2 (patched): ...
* gmp (older versions in many repos):

For pckaging
* pyinstaller


OS-specific hints:
----------------------------------

==== Ubuntu 12.04/12.10/13.04

$ sudo apt-get install libmpc-dev libmpfr-dev build-essential m4 python-dev python libboost-python-dev libboost-system-dev python-crypto python-gmpy python-scipy
$ cd src && make && make test

===== OSX 10.6+
* Install XCode: https://developer.apple.com/xcode/

!! It is possible to build boost manually and use the OSX python.
!! However, it is much easier to use Homebrew to install all dependencies.

* Install Homebrew: http://mxcl.github.io/homebrew/
$ brew install boost
$ brew install python
$ pip install pycrypto
$ pip install gmpy
$ cd src && make && make test
